text: Charity Wakefield (born 18 September 1980) is an English actress. She is known for her roles in Sense & Sensibility (2008), Casualty 1900s (2008–2009), Wolf Hall, Close to the Enemy (2016), Genius and Bounty Hunters (2017), and as Georgina Dymova in The Great (2020–2023). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from Kent
